{"word":"G4170 - πολεμέω - poleméō - pol-em-eh'-o - Fight","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">πολεμέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">poleméō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">pol-em-eh'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Fight</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - யுத்தம் பண்ணு"},{"paragraph":"to war, carry on war; to fight"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G4171 - πόλεμος - pólemos - pol'-em-os/4171\">G4171</a>; to <i>be</i> (engaged) in <i>warfare</i>, that is, to <i>battle</i> (literally or figuratively): - fight, (make) war.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G4170/4170\">G4170</a>, <a href=\"#/G4171/4171\">G4171</a>"}]}